<figureCitation box="[933,1005,767,793]" captionStart="FIGURES 2–13" captionStartId="19.[264,382,1747,1771]" captionTargetBox="[308,1278,313,1719]" captionTargetId="figure-78@19.[284,1300,310,1728]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURES 2–13. Brachylinga spp. tergite 8, epandrium, cerci, hypoproct, dorsal view. 2. albifrons. 3. albiseta. 4. attenuata. 5. baccata. 6. bicolor. 7. chilensis. 8. cinerea. 9. clausa. 10. concava. 11. curacaoensis. 12. divaricata. 13. fraterna. Scale = 0.1 mm. Abbreviations: C = cercus, Epa = epandrium, Hpt = hypoproct, SS = sensory seta, T8 = tergite 8." pageId="34" pageNumber="35">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
